    "rendered": "<p><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-148430\" src=\"http://www.extremetech.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/tesla-model-s-sunset-640x353.jpg\" alt=\"Tesla Model S, on a beach, at sunset. Nice.\" width=\"640\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://www.extremetech.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/tesla-model-s-sunset-640x353.jpg 640w, https://www.extremetech.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/tesla-model-s-sunset-300x165.jpg 300w, https://www.extremetech.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/tesla-model-s-sunset-106x59.jpg 106w, https://www.extremetech.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/tesla-model-s-sunset.jpg 672w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></p><p>Here at ExtremeTech, we take our automobiles very seriously. We&#8217;ve committed to bringing our readers coverage that&#8217;s focused on the automobile as a technology platform, and this guide is that result of that commitment. In the Auto Guide we&#8217;ll identify industry-leading tech as well as best-in-class automobiles, always bring you a thorough explanation of the technology and the rationale behind our choices.</p><h3>Understanding advanced automotive technology</h3><ul><li><span style=\"line-height: 13px;\"><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/157172-what-is-adaptive-cruise-control-and-how-does-it-work\">Adaptive cruise control explained</a><br /></span></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/165320-what-is-lane-departure-warning-and-how-does-it-work\">What is lane departure warning, and how does it work?</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/161815-electric-vehicles-vs-hybrids-its-all-about-the-egallon\">Electric vehicles vs. hybrids: It’s all about the eGallon</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/165742-blind-spot-detection-car-tech-that-watches-where-you-cant\">Blind spot detection: Car tech that watches where you can’t</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/193402-what-is-night-vision-how-does-it-work-and-do-i-really-need-it-in-my-next-car\">What is automotive night vision, and do you really need it on your next car?</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/170763-auto-tech-gas-vs-diesel-vs-hybrid-which-is-best-for-you-and-the-environment\">Gas vs. hybrid. vs. electric</a></li></ul><h3>ExtremeTech&#8217;s best-in-class (by category)</h3><ul><li><strong>Best luxury car:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/161832-2014-mercedes-s-class-review-the-best-most-technologically-advanced-car-you-will-ever-drive\">2014 Mercedes S-Class</a></li><li><span style=\"line-height: 13px;\"><strong>Best high-end SUV:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/193731-2015-bmw-x5-suv-review-the-best-grand-touring-car-with-the-most-technology\">2015 BMW X5</a></span></li><li><strong>Best small SUV</strong>: <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/159451-subaru-forester-best-small-suv\">2014 Subaru Forester</a></li><li><strong>Best midsize sports sedan: </strong><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/179913-2015-hyundai-genesis-review-the-best-tech-at-the-best-price-bar-none\">2015 Hyundai Genesis</a></li><li><strong>Best midsize hybrid:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/164071-2014-ford-fusion-hybrid-review-best-midsize-hybrid-in-a-crowded-field\">2014 Ford Fusion</a></li><li><strong>Best mainstream full-size:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/169499-2014-chevrolet-impala-review-your-gm-bailout-dollars-were-very-well-spent-indeed\">2014 Chevrolet Impala</a></li><li><strong>Best mainstream sedan:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/185492-2015-hyundai-sonata-review-driver-assistance-makes-this-the-best-midsize-sedan-made-today\">2015 Hyundai Sonata</a></li><li><strong>Best mainstream compact:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/185631-car-review-mazda3-best-tech-compact-is-also-the-best-handling-small-car\">2014 Mazda3</a></li><li><strong>Best small car:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173190-2014-bmw-3-series-review-50-mpg-and-the-best-small-car-for-tech-and-driver-assistance\">2014 BMW 3 Series</a></li><li><strong>Best subcompact: </strong><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/180232-2015-honda-fit-review-best-subcompact-for-tech-but-not-the-cheapest\">2015 Honda Fit</a></li><li><strong>Best supercar:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/191020-2015-bmw-i8-review-the-first-eco-friendly-supercar\">2015 BMW i8</a></li></ul><h3>2014 reviews</h3><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/167786-2014-chevrolet-cruze-diesel-review\">2014 Chevrolet Cruze diesel</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/167482-mercedes-benz-cla-reviewed-the-best-22-sports-car-for-30000-or-40k-with-tech\">2014 Mercedes-Benz CLA</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/170064-2014-nissan-rogue-review-bigger-plusher-more-tech-still-under-30000\">2014 Nissan Rogue</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/171032-2014-chevrolet-spark-ev-review-electric-motor-50-navigation-wash-away-sins-of-the-gas-version\">2014 Chevrolet Spark EV</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/171812-2014-honda-civic-review-an-almost-hud-without-the-1000-upcharge\">2014 Honda Civic</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173827-2014-hyundai-equus-review-like-a-lexus-ls-only-cheaper-with-unique-technology\">2014 Hyundai Equus</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/176728-2014-toyota-highlander-review-great-midsize-suv-but-limited-tech-under-45k\">2014 Toyota Highlander</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/176471-2014-cadillac-cts-review-top-notch-performance-but-not-ease-of-use\">2014 Cadillac CTS</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/175682-2014-hyundai-santa-fe-review-driver-friendly-tech-makes-it-worth-the-wait\">2014 Hyundai Santa Fe</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173908-2014-ford-fiesta-st-review-subcompact-thats-a-hot-rod-at-heart\">2014 Ford Fiesta ST</a></li></ul><h3>Earlier reviews</h3><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/163420-2013-honda-fit-review-a-good-small-car-with-amazing-cup-holders-but-modest-tech\">2013 Honda Fit</a></li></ul><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-122295\" src=\"http://www.extremetech.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/McLaren-MP4-12C-dihedral-doors.jpg\" alt=\"McLaren MP4-12C dihedral doors\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://www.extremetech.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/McLaren-MP4-12C-dihedral-doors.jpg 640w, https://www.extremetech.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/McLaren-MP4-12C-dihedral-doors-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></p><h3>ExtremeTech&#8217;s best tech cars</h3><ul><li><strong><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013\">Best tech cars of 2013</a></strong><ul><li><em>2013 Car of the Year: <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013\">Mercedes-Benz S-Class</a></em></li><li>Runner-up: <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/2\">Chevrolet Impala</a></li><li>Runner-up: <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/3\">Tesla Model S</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/4\">Acura RLX Hybrid</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/5\">Audi A6 and A8</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/6\">BMW 3 Series</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/7\">Chevrolet Silverado and GMC Sierra</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/8\">Ford C-Max and Focus</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/9\">Nissan Versa Note SV</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/10\">Subaru Forester</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/173417-10-best-tech-cars-2013/11\">Honorable mentions</a>: Chevrolet Cruze diesel, Chevrolet Sonic, Ford Flex, Ford Fusion hybrid, Honda Accord, Honda Civic, Honda Odyssey, Nissan Rogue, Mercedes-Benz GL, Toyota Prius</li></ul></li></ul><ul><li><strong><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012\"><span style=\"line-height: 13px;\">Best tech cars of 2012</span></a></strong><ul><li><em>2012 Car of the Year: <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012\">Tesla Model S</a></em></li><li>Runner-up: <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/2\">Audi A6</a></li><li>Runner-up: <a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/3\">BMW 3 Series</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/4\">Chevrolet Sonic</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/5\">Ford Focus/C-Max</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/6\">Honda Accord</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/7\">Infiniti JX35/Nissan Pathfinder</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/8\">Mercedes Benz GL</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/9\">Nissan Altima</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/10\">Toyota Prius</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/143887-10-best-tech-cars-of-2012/11\">Honorable mentions</a>: Dodge Dart, Cadillac ATS, Cadillac XTS, Hyundai Elanta, Hyundai Azera, Subura Legacy, Subaru Outback, Ford Fusion, Volvo XC60</li></ul></li><li><strong><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012\">Best tech cars of 2011</a></strong><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012\">Ford Focus</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/2\">Audi A7</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/3\">BMW 5 Series</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/4\">GMC Terrain</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/5\">Honda Odyssey</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/6\">Hyundai Elanta</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/7\">Nissan Leaf</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/8\">Volvo X60</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/9\">Toyota Prius</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/111269-10-best-tech-cars-for-2012/10\">VW Passat</a></li></ul></li></ul><h3>Auto tech we&#8217;re excited about</h3><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/tag/self-driving-cars\">Self-driving cars</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/158404-gorilla-glass-coming-to-cars\"><span style=\"line-height: 13px;\">Gorilla Glass windshields</span></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/158408-recharge-your-electric-vehicle-in-20-minutes-starting-later-this-year\">20-minute battery recharges</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/154674-intels-new-car-headlamp-makes-rain-and-snow-almost-invisible\">Intel&#8217;s futuristic headlamps make snow and rain disappear</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/151801-aluminium-air-battery-can-power-electric-vehicles-for-1000-miles-will-come-to-production-cars-in-2017\">1000-mile aluminum-air batteries</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/131485-digital-dashboard-why-your-cars-next-instrument-panel-will-be-one-big-lcd\">More big LCDs</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/133549-inside-virttex-fords-amazing-driver-distraction-simulator\">Advanced driver simulators</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/tag/flying-cars\">Flying cars</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/189512-your-3d-printed-car-will-be-ready-to-drive-in-44-hours\">3D-printed cars</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/192863-ford-and-honda-stop-collisions-before-they-happen-with-pedestrian-detection\">Pedestrian detection and collision avoidance</a></li></ul>",
